org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface MovingAverage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Documentable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MovingAverageImpl

    public interface MovingAverage
extends Documentable
    A representation of the model object 'Moving Average'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Item
    • Range
    • Null Range
    • Trigger
    • Trigger Only

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getMovingAverage()

      • getTrigger

        long getTrigger()
        Returns the value of the 'Trigger' attribute. The default value is "1". A period time in seconds when the average will be updated although no value has changed.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Trigger' attribute.

      • getTriggerOnly

        java.lang.Boolean getTriggerOnly()
        Returns the value of the 'Trigger Only' attribute. The default value is "false". A flag which decides if the average is only updated by time (true) or also by value change (false).
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Trigger Only' attribute.
        See Also:
        setTriggerOnly(Boolean), OsgiPackage.getMovingAverage_TriggerOnly()
